high_descs: Walk straight and turn left after entering into another room, make a few terms to stand facing the left side of the diningtable.
Pick up the bowl having potato from the table.
Make an exit out of the room and then turn left two times to enter into the adjacent room, make your way to the sidetable lying along with the bed.
Put the bowl on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Bring the Bowl of Potato into the bedroom

high_descs: Walk straight to enter the dining room and face the right of the diningtable.
Pick the bowl with the potato from the table.
Exit the room and walk to the bedroom on the left and face the sidetable on the left.
Put the bowl on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the Potato in the Bowl on the SideTable.

high_descs: Walk towards and turn left and turn around the diningtable.
Turn right and pick the potato with the bowl on the table.
Turn around and turn right and turn left near the sidetable in the bedroom.
Place the potato with plate on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: To place the potato with bowl on the sidetable.
